{"tid":35932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"疑閃粉致逾10人皮膚敏感 摸BANDAI遊戲卡 癌童手腫送院","createTime":"2016-12-12T11:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-08T23:06:50.000Z","uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf5bdf331b2cfa76fb9822a992826a2fd843574","tid":35932,"uid":39181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:35:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161212/19862775?_ga=1.164690811.519622040.1470297210\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161212%2F19862775%3F_ga%3D1.164690811.519622040.1470297210&d=XgYSpDQkWPfYcZ3%2BIBN8pHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e96a194c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161212%2F19862775%3F_ga%3D1.164690811.519622040.1470297210&h=b141a454\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161212/19862775?_ga=1.164690811.519622040.1470297210</a><br />\n【本報訊】跳舞遊戲「星夢學園」在港日大熱，多名女粉絲昨在荔枝角購買全新遊戲卡並即場試玩，<span style=\"color: red;\">其間引起10多人報稱皮膚敏感、手掌紅腫、臉部或眼睛痕癢等，至少8人送院，包括12歲患癌女童</span>。有事主引述醫生指懷疑「劣質化學劑」引致敏感，考慮報警追究責任，並呼籲停售有關遊戲卡，以策安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161212/small/12la7p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161212%2Fsmall%2F12la7p11.jpg&h=cf62a098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其中一名不適的24歲姓韓女子，自稱是BANDAI遊戲星夢學園忠實擁躉，她指玩家要購買遊戲卡後替角色換衣服等，她透露香港代理商過去兩日分別在荔枝角碧海藍天及康怡的AEON店舉行聖誕派對，以每包特價14.9元出售最新一季的遊戲卡（一包3張、表面有疑似金粉)，她和好友昨參加即買即玩。<br />\n<br />\n手部感痛楚灼熱<br />\n但韓女表示，接觸遊戲卡不久，發現有甩金粉的情況，她並覺得手部有痛楚灼熱，其後手掌更紅腫起來，有其他玩家亦出現不同程度的皮膚敏感，例如手腳、面部或眼睛紅腫及痕癢。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">其中過敏反應最嚴重是一名12歲患肝癌女童，她一度身體顫抖，率先被送院及打針。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n至傍晚6時許，韓女等6名女子（11至24歲）亦因感不適報警，由兩輛救護車送明愛醫院救治，加上另一名男事主，韓女稱前後合共至少8人送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家連玩隻卡game都咁危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6749adb52b6ccea092884bc3ac36e7435d47fa","tid":35932,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不安<br />\n係咪樓下班𡃁妹玩個部機？"},{"pid":"928a11719afea53e2eab9828bf67f9bb15e663e9","tid":35932,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不安<br />\n係咪樓下班𡃁妹玩個部機？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓下有兩部，成日見啲𡃁妹玩"},{"pid":"c7341a066117f48ceaee6b1694963b743c3aac5c","tid":35932,"uid":30900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"個肝癌女童冇事嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c07f3e9908664d76767737b085a9824a9026a1","tid":35932,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-08T23:06:50.000Z","msg":"ด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้( ͡&deg; ͜ʖ͡&deg;)ด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้<br />\nด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้( ͡&deg; ͜ʖ͡&deg;)ด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้<br />\nด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้( ͡&deg; ͜ʖ͡&deg;)ด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้<br />\nด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้( ͡&deg; ͜ʖ͡&deg;)ด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้<br />\nด้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้้้้็็็็็้้้้้็็็็็้้( ͡&deg; ͜ʖ͡&deg;)ด้้้้้็็็็็้้